  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682200/extras/693b4365588e49cb50a811d2aa815f2a.poster.avif?t=1658941825\" width=700 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682200/extras/693b4365588e49cb50a811d2aa815f2a.webm?t=1658941825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682200/extras/693b4365588e49cb50a811d2aa815f2a.mp4?t=1658941825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>BJORN is a rpg-platformer with a linear and dramatic storyline. You must save your family, which was kidnapped by your brother, our protagonist. As you progress through the story, you will learn the story of the enmity between the two brothers.<br>The name of our hero is Bjorn, a Viking who skillfully wields his ax. On his way, he will meet a large number of enemies, magic and traps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682200/extras/0a8b607f8dcbd9cc75239292786f2383.poster.avif?t=1658941825\" width=700 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682200/extras/0a8b607f8dcbd9cc75239292786f2383.webm?t=1658941825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682200/extras/0a8b607f8dcbd9cc75239292786f2383.mp4?t=1658941825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682200/extras/2cefd5205b18cd8a35c1459abe5c57ea.poster.avif?t=1658941825\" width=700 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682200/extras/2cefd5205b18cd8a35c1459abe5c57ea.webm?t=1658941825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682200/extras/2cefd5205b18cd8a35c1459abe5c57ea.mp4?t=1658941825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682200/extras/1ec662c946440d95497baf87b6e8db93.poster.avif?t=1658941825\" width=700 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682200/extras/1ec662c946440d95497baf87b6e8db93.webm?t=1658941825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682200/extras/1ec662c946440d95497baf87b6e8db93.mp4?t=1658941825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
